Reasoning: The paper deals with the capacity limits of UAV-enabled multiuser communication systems, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The optimization of the UAV's trajectory and transmit power/rate allocations over time falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of superposition coding (SC), which is a technique commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) communication systems.
